Speedy
Copyright (c) 2013 John Peloquin. All rights reserved.

Speedy measures the speed of an internet connection. It is useful for keeping internet service providers honest.

Requirements: phantomjs

Speedy uses the SpeedOf.Me service for speed testing.

WARNING: USE OF SPEEDY MAY OR MAY NOT CONSTITUTE A VIOLATION OF THE TERMS OF
         SERVICE OF THE SPEEDOF.ME SERVICE OR YOUR INTERNET SERVICE PROVIDER.
         PLEASE CONSULT THE TERMS OF SERVICE WITH QUALIFIED LEGAL COUNSEL
         PRIOR TO USE. THE AUTHORS OF SPEEDY ASSUME NO LIABILITY FOR ITS USE.
